HEADWORD: love-potion
<hw>love-potion</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a fabled drink credited with
magical power; it can make the one who takes it love the one who gave
it.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> philter, philtre, love-philter,
love-philtre.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lover</ent>⟦br⟧
